document_data.name: Moon Corn
document_data.mainbody: '''Moon corn''' was a strain of [[corn]] characterized by its crescent-shaped kernels.
document_data.Availability: Moon corn was first cultivated in [[Vaasa]]. By the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]], it had been adopted in [[Sembia]], where it was grown alongside regular corn. Despite not being native to [[interior Faer√ªn]], moon corn had no noticeable negative impacts on the local environment.
